Element


member
&member.purpose;


&member.synopsis.gen;
Description



A Member is an element of a SimpleList.  Unlike
the other lists, items in a SimpleList are constrained to 
character data and inline elements.


Processing expectations


&format.inline; How the inline Members are formatted
with respect to each other is controlled by the containing
SimpleList.



